      <title>胡塞武装视频显示红海油轮泄漏发生爆炸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/houthi-video-shows-bombs-set-off-on-ship-leaking-oil-in-red-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗支持的胡塞武装公布了一段视频，显示蒙面人员登上“苏尼翁号”油轮并引爆炸弹。“苏尼翁号”悬挂希腊国旗，在红海遭到袭击后正在等待打捞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/houthi-video-shows-bombs-set-off-on-ship-leaking-oil-in-red-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 05:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
